--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1. gpshub general info
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

gpshub - is a server designed to allow sharing gps positions

            .-----------.
    .------>|  gpshub   |<-----.
    |       '-----------'      |
 .-----.          ^         .-----.
 | gps |          |         | gps |
 '-----'          |         '-----'
               .-----.
               | gps |
               '-----'

gps - application using gps device which shares position with others


 .------------.             .--------.
 |   gpshub   |<----TCP-----|  gps   |
 |            |<----UDP-----|        |
 '------------'             '--------'

TCP - command channel
UDP - gps position channel

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

